### Start analysis (global market)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repoUrl": "https://github.com/MedouneSGB/flash-transfer",
  "market": "global"
}

### Start analysis (local market with location)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repoUrl": "https://github.com/MedouneSGB/flash-transfer",
  "market": "local",
  "location": "Dakar"
}

### Stream analysis progress (replace {{jobId}} with the value from the POST response)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/analyze/{{jobId}}/stream
Accept: text/event-stream

### Get final report
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/analyze/{{jobId}}/report
Accept: application/json

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8083/actuator/health
